<p>As the company grew and more employers onboard in the company, it was crucial to have a source of truth on design and component rules. The company created Solaris to keep all products under Codebots in harmony.</p>

<p>The goal behind this is for everyone, especially developers to come to a website and view rules of design but also components. These components are documented by design, usage and code usage.</p>

<p>The website had to be clear, and easy to navigate to the right content.</p>
